24  const Tad dvdx = val_grad_v[i][j][0];
25  const Tad dvdy = val_grad_v[i][j][1];
26 
27  const Tad dTdx = val_grad_T[i][j][0];
28  const Tad dTdy = val_grad_T[i][j][1];
29 
30  const Tad ubar = val_ubar[i][j];
31  const Tad vbar = val_vbar[i][j];
32 
33  const Tad mu = val_mubar[i][j];
34  const Tad k = val_kbar[i][j];
35 
36  const Tad tau_xy = mu*(dudy + dvdx);
37  const Tad tau_xx = mu*(2.0*dudx - 2.0/3.0*(dudx + dvdy));
38  const Tad tau_yy = mu*(2.0*dvdy - 2.0/3.0*(dudx + dvdy));
39  const Tad q_x = -k*dTdx;
40  const Tad q_y = -k*dTdy;
41 
42  val_flux[i][j][0] = 0.0;
43  val_flux[i][j][1] = tau_xx*nx + tau_xy*ny;
44  val_flux[i][j][2] = tau_xy*nx + tau_yy*ny;
45  val_flux[i][j][3] = (ubar*tau_xx + vbar*tau_xy - q_x)*nx + (ubar*tau_xy + vbar*tau_yy - q_y)*ny;
46  }
47  }

72  const Tad vrht = vrht_a[i][j];
73  const Tad prht = prht_a[i][j];

75  const Tad rlfti = 1.0/rlft;
76  const Tad rulft = rlft*ulft;
77  const Tad rvlft = rlft*vlft;
78  const Tad uvl = 0.5*(ulft*ulft + vlft*vlft);
79  const Tad elft = plft*ogm1 + rlft*uvl;
80  const Tad hlft = (elft + plft)*rlfti;
81 
82

86  const Tad uvr = 0.5*(urht*urht + vrht*vrht);
87  const Tad erht = prht*ogm1 + rrht*uvr;
88  const Tad hrht = (erht + prht)*rrhti;
89 
90  const Tad rat = sqrt(rrht*rlfti);
91  const Tad rati = 1.0/(rat+1.0);
92  const Tad rav = rat*rlft;
93  const Tad uav = (rat*urht + ulft)*rati;
94  const Tad vav = (rat*vrht + vlft)*rati;
95  const Tad hav = (rat*hrht + hlft)*rati;
96  const Tad uv = 0.5*(uav*uav + vav*vav);
97  const Tad cav = sqrt(gm1*(hav - uv));
98 
99  Tad aq1 = rrht - rlft;
100  Tad aq2 = urht - ulft;
101  Tad aq3 = vrht - vlft;
102  Tad aq4 = prht - plft;
103 
104  const Tad dr = sqrt(nx*nx + ny*ny);
105  const Tad r1 = nx/dr;
106  const Tad r2 = ny/dr;
107 
108 
109  const Tad uu = r1*uav + r2*vav;
110  const Tad c2 = cav*cav;
111  const Tad c2i = 1.0/c2;
112  const Tad auu = fabs(uu);
113  const Tad aupc = fabs(uu + cav);
114  const Tad aumc = fabs(uu - cav);
115 
116  const Tad uulft = r1*ulft + r2*vlft;
117  const Tad uurht = r1*urht + r2*vrht;
118  const Tad rcav = rav*cav;
119  const Tad aquu = uurht - uulft;
120  const Tad c2ih = 0.5*c2i;
121  const Tad ruuav = auu*rav;
122 
123  const Tad b1 = auu*(aq1 - c2i*aq4);
124  const Tad b2 = c2ih*aupc*(aq4 + rcav*aquu);
125  const Tad b3 = c2ih*aumc*(aq4 - rcav*aquu);
126  const Tad b4 = b1 + b2 + b3;
127  const Tad b5 = cav*(b2 - b3);
128  const Tad b6 = ruuav*(aq2 - r1*aquu);
129  const Tad b7 = ruuav*(aq3 - r2*aquu);
130 
131  aq1 = b4;
132  aq2 = uav*b4 + r1*b5 + b6;
133  aq3 = vav*b4 + r2*b5 + b7;
134  aq4 = hav*b4 + uu*b5 + uav*b6 + vav*b7 - c2*b1*ogm1;
135 
136  const Tad aj = 0.5*dr;
137  const Tad plar = plft + prht;
138  const Tad eplft = elft + plft;
139  const Tad eprht = erht + prht;
140  f_a[i][j][0] = aj*(rlft*uulft + rrht*uurht - aq1);
141  f_a[i][j][1] = aj*(rulft*uulft + rurht*uurht + r1*plar - aq2);
142  f_a[i][j][2] = aj*(rvlft*uulft + rvrht*uurht + r2*plar - aq3);
143  f_a[i][j][3] = aj*(eplft*uulft + eprht*uurht - aq4);
144  }
145  }
